        <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_marginHorizontal="@dimen/text_margin"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text=" A unique feature of our college is the emphasis given co-curricular and extra-curricular activities. Each department has a study forum attached to it through which seminars, lectures quiz programmes are held through out the year. Eminent resource persons are invited from outside to deliver special lectures. Through such interactions, we hope to expose the students to the concept of learning beyond the classroom. We have a unit of N.C.C.and two units of N.S.S. There is a student forum comprising of student representatives, which organises many co-curricular activities.We conduct a course in art appreciation 'AAKRITI' every year in which students are exposed to various art forms like literature, music.dance.drama,ms and plastic arts, we also have Film Club, Red Cross Unit, women's grievance redressel cell Student Counseling Center and Placement cell. Traditional day is celebrated every year to exhibit the traditional of Indian culture society."
            android:textAlignment="textStart"
            android:textSize="@dimen/text_size2"
            android:layout_marginVertical="10dp"
            android:fontFamily="@font/latoregular"/>


